					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">No, the number you write to $4014 specifies the upper byte of the address that DMA reads from. (i.e. writing 2 means it transfers $0200 to $02ff; writing $81 means it transfers $8100 to $81ff, &amp;c)</div>

