				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">A lot of games use $0200-$02FF. A lot of other games use $0700-$07FF. Some games with extra RAM on the cartridge use one of the pages in $6000-$7FFF. <em>Hot Seat Harry</em> uses $0000-$00FF so that it can write to shadow OAM using shorter zero page instructions; it hides other zero page variables from the sprite processor with $Fx.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

